(157, 1, '2021-10-19 02:51:07', '2021-10-19 02:51:07', '2021-10-19', '02:44:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my college was', 'In Database class, I learnt more about joins. In Data Structures 1 class, I learnt about operations and time. In Precalculus class, I learnt about stretching and shrinking. In Fundamentals of Speech class, I learnt about speaking in the right tone and more about giving a speech.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
