(165, 1, '2021-10-24 13:40:33', '2021-10-24 13:56:14', '2021-10-24', '13:34:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'My friend from Atlantic Beach blocked me', 'My friend from Atlantic Beach blocked me. Iâ€™m going to go back to Atlantic Beach to find out whatâ€™s going on. I asked him directly on ×©×‘×ª if I made him uncomfortable and he said â€œnoâ€. I texted him last night when ×©×‘×ª was over â€œhow was your afternoon?â€ And not only does he not respond but he blocked me. This politely declining thing just doesnâ€™t work with me. I feel like blocking is an offense to me. I want to know exactly what I did that made him uncomfortable. This is not an isolated incident because this happened with my friend in Boca Raton, Florida as well as other friends ghosting me. All I want is a friend. Why canâ€™t people just be straight out with me. I\'m actually very shocked about this because I told my friend Friday night that my friend from Florida blocked me and he told me \"He blocked you!? That\'s terrible! Is he Jewish?\". I just don\'t understand why he would hurt me like that.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(166, 1, '2021-10-25 00:03:59', '2021-10-25 00:03:59', '2021-10-24', '23:51:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'I finally figured out the reason why my new friends keep blocking me', 'I finally figured out the reason why my new friends keep blocking me. I got a call from the person who introduced me to the friend in Atlantic Beach and told me that his mother was the one that told him to block me. He told me that him and the mother was very petrified of me that I keep on being so attached to my friends like I had that relationship for 15 years when I just met him. I only see what a friend is from my siblings friends so I thought that acting the same towards my friends would be okay but it wasnâ€™t. I have a feeling it was the same way with my other friends that Iâ€™m making my friends and the parents very uncomfortable by being so attached to my friends. I wish I would have siblings that are beginners on relationships so I can learn from them instead of being with siblings that are so advanced. Iâ€™m happy that thereâ€™s finally closure on this and to know that I need to keep my distance next time. Iâ€™m going to go to North Woodmere on Tuesday and have very little expectations. I will definitely not expect myself to be as close as their other friends. The person who just called me that introduced me to that latest friend will be nice enough to help me through this. I asked him if my latest friendship is over and he told me â€œdid it even start yet?â€.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(167, 1, '2021-10-25 13:43:51', '2021-10-25 13:43:51', '2021-10-25', '13:38:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'People from the Jewish Center of Atlantic Beach are interested in helping me', 'People from the Jewish Center of Atlantic Beach are interested in helping me. I got a call from another person that attends the shul and told me that heâ€™s interested in helping me out with my friendships and problems and will be there for me. He told me to not text or call a lot like I did to my other friends. I need to text that person first if heâ€™s freely available to talk and provide the topic. He also is willing to work with my social worker on my problems and will give him my social workerâ€™s contact info when I either call the clinic or see my social worker next.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
