(180, 1, '2021-10-31 16:03:02', '2021-10-31 16:03:02', '2021-10-31', '13:00:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'Where I did ×ª×¤×™×œ×ª ×©×—×¨×™×ª this morning', 'I attempted to do ×©×—×¨×™×ª at the 7:30AM minyan at the Red Shul but there wasnâ€™t any. Someone helped me ask the Rabbi there about helping me find a friend with Aspergerâ€™s and said he will help and exchanged phone numbers with the person that helped me. I went to the 8AM minyan at the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
