(182, 1, '2021-11-01 00:29:32', '2021-11-01 00:34:32', '2021-11-01', '00:15:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'My experience to and in the Bach Shul of Long Beach', 'I walked to the Bach Shul in Long Beach for ×ž× ×—×”/×ž×¢×¨×™×‘. I walked over the Atlantic Beach bridge like I did when I went to the Jewish Center of Atlantic Beach but passed it. The streets in Atlantic Beach are in alphabetical order followed by The Sands and then East Atlantic Beach followed by Long Beach. After a while of walking, I saw a sign that said â€œWelcome to the city of Long Beachâ€. I didnâ€™t believe that it would be a real city until I walked a block in and wow was it congested. There was everything you can find in Manhattan including dogs and it was in middle of Halloween so it was more busy than ever. Even though I was in Long Beach, the shul was still far away because Long Beach is a big city, weirdly, smack in middle of a suburb. After a mile and a half of walking, I finally reached the Bach Shul in the dead center of Long Beach. Long Beach is divided between West Beech St and East Beech St and the Bach Shul was at the East Beech St side. I came to the Bach Shul a half an hour ahead of schedule. The walk was supposed to be an hour and 51 minutes but it was an hour and 25 minutes. I waited the half hour in front of the Bach Shul since it was locked until it opened up. It was a small Shul and there was no one my age at ×ž× ×—×”/×ž×¢×¨×™×‘ tonight and the Rabbi wasnâ€™t there also. I walked back home in the dark and here I am.', 'me-at-the-bach-shul.jpg', 1, 'Me at the Bach Shul', NULL, 1),
(183, 1, '2021-11-01 15:50:09', '2021-11-01 15:50:09', '2021-11-01', '15:40:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my morning was so far', 'I overslept but had no choice but to walk to Beth Sholom because I wanted to buy things at Gourmet Glatt before taking the train into work. I completely missed minyan and davened by myself at Beth Sholom. On the train, I was talking to the father of a friend I made uncomfortable with at the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst and was willing to help me a little and I gave him my mother\'s number. At work, I couldn\'t get any work done even with my Job Coach there and was busy explaining to her my anxiety and depression about the whole friend thing. After a lot of explaining and showing her my latest college grades which I did badly on because of anxiety and depression, she emailed my supervisor and even got a reply back reminding me of the Yachad bowling event this Thursday at 6PM which I\'m looking forward to but anxious about how it\'s going to go due to what happened with the past 5 friends I made (they either blocked or ghosted me). I might even start com hab again. I feel like I want to pause college but my parents will give me a lot of backlash for it thinking that it\'s a stupid decision and that I should move on with my life, finish college, and get a job and make friends at the workplace which I know wouldn\'t help and would, in matter of fact, be much worse because then they would report me for bothering them when I didn\'t mean to. I don\'t know the right way of how to go about making friends. Everything is pretty much black & white for me with no grey areas in between which makes it a problem and my parents just don\'t understand. My parents never even saw me with a friend before. They just see me with people that I\'m not really comfortable with due to their completely different schedule.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(184, 1, '2021-11-02 02:59:19', '2021-11-02 02:59:19', '2021-11-02', '02:51:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my college was', 'I came early to Database class to finish my exam. In database class, I learned about rollouts and other advanced functions. In Data Structures 1 class, I learned more about LinkedLists. In Precalculus class, the professor called another student up to explain tables to me. The professor then taught the class more about composition of functions and oh boy were there unions. In Fundamentals of Speech class, the professor talked about how to give a speech the right way and know your audience and that body language matters.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(185, 1, '2021-11-02 14:04:36', '2021-11-02 14:04:36', '2021-11-02', '13:52:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'My experience to, at, and back from the Young Israel of Long Beach', 'I overslept this morning. I meant to wake up at 5AM and instead woke up at 5:35AM. I walked fast to the Young Israel of Long Beach and got there 11 minutes late all sweated up. ×©×—×¨×™×ª was at 6:50AM and I came at 7:01AM. Unfortunately, not only was there no one with Aspergerâ€™s but there was no one my age there. I was prepared to walk home after ×©×—×¨×™×ª but Google Maps said that I would get home before 10AM and I needed to start work at 9AM so I waited for the 8:29AM n33 bus from Long Beach LIRR station, bought a mobile ticket for $2.75 with my transitchek card, and boarded the bus. It was an interesting bus ride and got back to Far Rockaway in 20 minutes and got off at the Beach 9 St & Seagirt Blvd stop. I walked back home from there. My mother wasnâ€™t so happy. She told me that sheâ€™s getting calls from people that itâ€™s weird that Iâ€™m going all over the place to find friends.', 'bus-from-long-beach.jpg', 1, 'Bus from Long Beach', NULL, 1),
(186, 1, '2021-11-02 21:37:42', '2021-11-02 21:39:13', '2021-11-02', '21:27:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'Iâ€™m starting to begin thinking that college is not for me', 'I donâ€™t really think that college is for me. Up until now, I was taught things I already knew but now Iâ€™m learning new things but I learn very differently. I learn by doing and not by listening to an hour and a half of lectures and reapplying it to the homework. Iâ€™m pretty much already behind on my homework. I have enough issues already with friendships and Iâ€™m getting into depression from all this homework without study groups. Someone told me that most colleges donâ€™t have study groups. Also, what do I gain with a computer science degree over a coding bootcamp? I would pretty much be making the same money due to my college not being as hard as a mainstream college. Iâ€™m not sure if I even do well under a boss and would be better at making a startup. College is just so much money and the loans keep on going up. I feel like a bootcamp would be more enjoyable. The problems are that my parents wonâ€™t be happy about this and kick me out of the house which they mentioned if I drop out of college and repaying back the loans and financial aid. Iâ€™m going to be speaking to a school counselor about this.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(187, 1, '2021-11-03 17:26:31', '2021-11-03 17:26:31', '2021-11-03', '17:13:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my day is going so far', 'I made it a little late to ×©×—×¨×™×ª in Beth Sholom but was still able to do ×ª×¤×™×œ×” with a minyan. I bought food for the day from Gourmet Glatt and took the LIRR into work. I had a call with the college counselor about dropping out of college and told me that it would have to be solved with the dean and that he\'ll get back to me. After that, I started getting very curious of what became of the other friend I made in Boca Raton. I have a feeling that I\'m being ghosted by him and sure enough after enough searching, I saw another YouTube channel with his voice on the videos that is active. Why do people have to disappear from me? Why can\'t they just tell me why they\'re not comfortable with me anymore so I can learn from this and improve. I\'m curious what exactly went wrong with those 2 people? It\'s very likely that it\'s the same situation as the friend I made from Atlantic Beach that I got blocked from. I pushed the friendship too hard. 2 people are already helping me on how to make friends the right way but I just want to confirm that this is the same situation as my friend from Atlantic Beach. No one owes me their friendship but they should at least understand what I\'m going through and tell me that they\'re not comfortable with me anymore because of so and so. Every failed friend is supposed to be a learning experience but if they\'re blocking or ghosting me with no explanation, then how should I learn from this and move on? Blocking and ghosting look like I\'m being politely declined but I don\'t think that\'s the case.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(188, 1, '2021-11-04 03:00:49', '2021-11-04 03:01:39', '2021-11-04', '02:50:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my college was', 'In database class, I learned about subqueries. The professor for Data Structures 1 wasnâ€™t there so he made a video for the class to watch. In Precalculus class, I learned about inverse functions. I was depressed in those 3 classes due to friend rejection as I was wanting to confirm that the other person from Boca Raton was indeed ghosting me and abandoning and making new accounts. In Fundamentals of Speech, everyone was practicing giving a speech. My medication wore off by then and I got into a hyper mood. I saw a twizzler on the desk and asked the professor what it was doing on the desk and he told me that itâ€™s for me (the photo of the completely finished twizzler wrapper is shown below).', 'finished-twizzler.jpg', 1, 'Finished twizzler', NULL, 1),
(189, 1, '2021-11-04 15:24:25', '2021-11-04 15:24:25', '2021-11-04', '15:20:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'Iâ€™m looking forward to the Yachad event tonight', 'Iâ€™m going to the Yachad bowling event tonight as a trial. Hopefully, Iâ€™ll make friends there. The event is at 6-7:30PM at Woodmere bowling lanes. I need to be very careful by making friends very slowly.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(190, 1, '2021-11-05 00:17:38', '2021-11-05 00:17:38', '2021-11-05', '00:09:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How the Yachad trial was', 'I walked to Woodmere Lanes for the Yachad trial event. It was pretty much teenagers. I did speak to a few people but remained cautious because of what happened with pushing friendships too hard. There was bowling, pizza, french fries, and soda. At the end, a counselor asked me how Iâ€™m getting home and I told her that Iâ€™m walking back home to Far Rockaway. She got suspicious about me walking back in the dark. I then told her that I walked back from Long Beach to Far Rockaway in the dark on Halloween and wondered if I was pranking her. I got a ride back with someone that lives in Bayswater.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
