(192, 1, '2021-11-07 00:08:49', '2021-11-07 00:08:49', '2021-11-06', '23:43:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my ×©×‘×ª was', 'I went to the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst for Friday night ×ª×¤×™×œ×” in the tent minyan hoping that there would be someone with Aspergerâ€™s in that minyan but there wasnâ€™t. I went to my neighbor across the street for the Friday night meal. I did ×©×—×¨×™×ª again at the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst and saw my friend this time. He told me that he started davening on weekdays also. I told him about the whole thing of people blocking me after texting them a lot and asked him if it annoyed him as well and he told me â€œto be honest, it doesâ€. He told me that it was annoying that he was being texted in middle of class and in the dorms and I apologized to him and told him to tell me next time this happens. I asked someone about the minyan in Mesivta Ateres Yaakov and he told me that itâ€™s a beautiful minyan. Iâ€™m a little scared about going there because 2 people there looked at me the wrong way and both blocked me. One of the people that blocked me was someone that I got set up with and actually got along very well and almost went to my high school (IVDU) but decided against it but told me that we can still be friends. I donâ€™t know what happened because we never exchanged phone numbers and I finally got his number 4 years later and asked him if he remembers me and he said no. I then tried everything I could to make him remember me and then he blocked me. I want to get to know him again. Someone else a little older than me that has Aspergerâ€™s came at the end of ×ª×¤×™×œ×” and I told him the whole story of people blocking me and he told me that people could be busy and donâ€™t appreciate being texted so much. I told him about me texting a friend where heâ€™s davening on ×©×‘×ª and he told me that every week is too much and that I should do it once a month.  I talked to him a little during ×§×™×“×•×© but I couldnâ€™t stay for s