(207, 1, '2021-11-14 00:29:05', '2021-11-14 00:30:16', '2021-11-14', '00:17:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'How my ×©×‘×ª was', 'I went to the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst for Friday night ×ª×¤×™×œ×” and said ×©×‘×ª ×©×œ×•× to Rabbi Trump after ×ª×¤×™×œ×”. I went back to the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst for ×©×—×¨×™×ª and asked advice from a father of someone with autism about how to make up with 2 people that blocked me that do ×ª×¤×™×œ×” at the minyan in Mesivta Ateres Yaakov. Thereâ€™s a friend that sometimes comes to the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst whoâ€™s father was there that told me that heâ€™s in Yeshiva University for ×©×‘×ª. I wish I would go to a program on ×©×‘×ª. I came home making a detour to someoneâ€™s house that has a mother that worked with someone who forgot about me and blocked me that goes to the minyan in MAY. Unfortunately, no one was home. I came back home late to the meal. Someone came to my house that Iâ€™m trying to be friends with. I did ×ž× ×—×” in the White Shul and stayed for ×©×¢×•×“×” ×©×œ×™×©×™×ª and ×ž×¢×¨×™×‘. I asked the Rabbi there if he knows someone with Aspergerâ€™s and he told that he knows someone and that heâ€™ll introduce me to someone. Someone else in the shul told me that heâ€™ll talk to a director of a camp to see if thereâ€™s someone with Aspergerâ€™s that I can connect with and will get back to me.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(208, 1, '2021-11-14 22:14:29', '2021-11-14 22:16:12', '2021-11-14', '21:55:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'A lot of people are upset at me already', 'I had a conversation with my parents last night about wanting to drop out of college and pause my education to improve my mental health and find friends and my parents said that Iâ€™m crazy for doing that. I recorded the whole conversation behind my parents back and sent it to some people including my training friend. My training friend got upset at me, saying that itâ€™s illegal to record someone. Another person told me to stop with this whole friend thing and get a life for myself. Iâ€™ve been complaining to a lot of people today, including my therapist, parents, and uncle and theyâ€™re all fed up with me about this. Iâ€™m just so frustrated because it used to be that I asked for someone my type that has Aspergerâ€™s and people were trying to tell me that I can be friends with people that donâ€™t have Aspergerâ€™s. Now itâ€™s getting worse with people saying to me that I donâ€™t have to be friends with people in my age bracket which just adds to my annoyance. Iâ€™ve been searching for friends for 7 years already and I just want to find a program with people my age that have disabilities but Iâ€™m too old for all the programs I know, like Aryehâ€™s adventures, which I just found out about last summer which maxes out at 22 years old. Someone told me that â€œthatâ€™s lifeâ€ and that I should just move on. I really want to have some fun, at least for a month, but I canâ€™t find any programs which are right for me. Either itâ€™s day hab, which is for low functioning people or moving on and getting a life for myself which Iâ€™m not ready for. Someoneâ€™s upset at me that their cousin is on a wild goose chase finding friends for me. People are having enough of me and all I want is a friend that I can enjoy spending time with. Iâ€™m actually very upset that my boss hired me since I never deserved my job in the first place. I cou