(209, 1, '2021-11-15 12:42:59', '2021-11-15 12:43:33', '2021-11-15', '12:39:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'Someone in Beth Sholom introduced me to Cognitive Behavior Intervention', 'Someone in Beth Sholom introduced me to Cognitive Behavior Intervention. He told me about how I interpreted behaviors the wrong way, for example, thinking that that person from my high school hates me because he stared at me the wrong way, when really, heâ€™s just shy. He told me that thereâ€™s an in-person session in Connecticut and thereâ€™s also one online. I would like to give it a try.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
